{"tid":1235812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新鴻基地產郭基煇：歡迎修訂《逃犯條例》 相信對集團無影響","createTime":"2019-06-17T09:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T11:33:54.000Z","uid":10540,"like":1,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"37b735ee227d33d26cd15a2a8455009f918a33ae","tid":1235812,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:04:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190606/s00001/b8d55dbfefcaec786db1282770295294.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190606%2Fs00001%2Fb8d55dbfefcaec786db1282770295294.jpg&h=9bab5a19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n修訂《逃犯條例》爭議不絕。新地執董、郭炳江兒子郭基煇透過發言人表示歡迎修例，並相信修例對集團無影響。<br />\n<br />\n郭基煇稱，留意到最近政府就修訂草案作出一些修改，認為修改顯示了政府回應社會意見的誠意，相信有助進一步釋除公眾疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n郭基煇又期望各方在尊重「一國兩制」前提下，以理性和客觀態度討論修訂《逃犯條例》，呼籲各界以務實態度排除分歧，尋找共識。未來會繼續大量投資香港及內地，支持香港及內地發展。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190606/s00001/1559812743676/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E6%96%B0%E5%9C%B0%E9%83%AD%E5%9F%BA%E7%85%87-%E6%AD%A1%E8%BF%8E%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B-%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%A1%E5%B0%8D%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98%E7%84%A1%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF?fbclid=IwAR1OuEgp-xyYM7gXQyQvBN5a_kf0DnmAqctPmrfaZ4cOoP4ZvKgLuI0f5xY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190606%2Fs00001%2F1559812743676%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%2583%25AD%25E5%259F%25BA%25E7%2585%2587-%25E6%25AD%25A1%25E8%25BF%258E%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E7%259B%25B8%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%259B%2586%25E5%259C%2598%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1OuEgp-xyYM7gXQyQvBN5a_kf0DnmAqctPmrfaZ4cOoP4ZvKgLuI0f5xY&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0u67%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=831e2587\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25